## Configuration Summary by Layer | Résumé par couche

### Access Layer
- VLAN segmentation  
- DHCP Snooping  
- STP Rapid-PVST  

### Distribution Layer
- HSRP (gateway redundancy)  
- Layer 3 EtherChannel  
- EIGRP AS 100  

### Core Layer
- EIGRP ↔ OSPF redistribution  
- Redundant links  

### ASA
- OSPF enabled  
- Failover configured  
- DMZ integration  

### FortiGate
- OSPF + BGP  
- SD-WAN  
- Dual ISP NAT  

### Transit Routers
- iBGP between R1/R2  
- eBGP to ISPs  
